ment pieces while conquering ferocious monsters and activating powerful perks along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766450/extras/1684ff46442188b26846b26a7858081c.webp?t=1715147340\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766450/extras/58a4a5a02629bd77d13e4479f0e8ec27.poster.avif?t=1715147340\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766450/extras/58a4a5a02629bd77d13e4479f0e8ec27.webm?t=1715147340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766450/extras/58a4a5a02629bd77d13e4479f0e8ec27.mp4?t=1715147340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>★Engage with numerous NPCs who are not just mere bystanders but possess abilities that can turn the tide in battle. Team up, strategize, and unleash devastating combos alongside these invaluable allies.<br><br>[Key Features]<br>★Intense battles with Boss/Elite class enemies<br>★Diverse role-builds with different gameplay styles<br>★Hundreds of equipment to collect, monsters to conquer and perks to activate<br>★NPCs have the ability to help the player before or during the battle<br>★Very well balanced game mechanics for challengers<br>★Top level BGM to make the player sink into the gameplay deeply<br>★Unexpected game ending<br>★In-depth game manual<br>★Immerse yourself in 20+ hours of gameplay and conquer 44 rewarding achievements<br>★No repetitive farming or grinding design",
